<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sejtautomaták Webalkalmazás</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #1e1e2f;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .container p {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .container a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .container a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .button-group {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .background {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, 60px);
            grid-gap: 5px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hexagon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 34.64px;
            background-color: yellow;
            position: relative;
            margin: 17.32px 0;
            clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 25%, 100% 75%, 50% 100%, 0% 75%, 0% 25%);
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 34.64px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: red;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .hexagon:nth-child(odd) {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background">
        <div class="hexagon">15</div>
        <div class="hexagon">13</div>
        <div class="hexagon">6</div>
        <div class="hexagon">5</div>
        <div class="hexagon">12</div>
        <div class="hexagon">18</div>
        <div class="hexagon">7</div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Üdvözlünk a Sejtautomaták Világában!</h1>
        <p>Fedezd fel a sejtautomaták lenyűgöző működését, például a "Game of Life" modelleken keresztül.</p>
        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="login.php">Bejelentkezés</a>
            <a href="guest.php">Belépés vendégként</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
